Odaily Planet Daily News According to official news, BNB Chain recently announced that it has cooperated with major wallet providers to launch three MEV protection solutions, committed to helping users protect their transactions from sandwich attacks and get a safer DeFi trading experience. The three solutions are: 
-Wallet with automatic MEV protection (enabled by default); 
-Wallet with manual MEV protection option; 
-Customized protection for advanced users. 
CZ posted on X about this progress: "Step by step."
